<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,602,1973,1998]" pageId="17" pageNumber="522">
Condition of the 
<typeStatus box="[400,464,1973,1998]" pageId="17" pageNumber="522">types</typeStatus>
. 
<typeStatus box="[476,596,1973,1998]" pageId="17" pageNumber="522">Lectotype</typeStatus>
.
</emphasis>
Wings slightly rubbed, left antenna broken. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1101,1273,1973,1998]" pageId="17" pageNumber="522">
