<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="523" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="18.[151,1436,151,248]" pageId="18" pageNumber="523">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,151,176]" pageId="18" pageNumber="523">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species was described from the specimens mentioned above. It most likely does not belong in 
<taxonomicName authority="Herrich-Schaffer, 1855" authorityName="Herrich-Schaffer" authorityYear="1855" box="[151,511,188,213]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Saurita" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="523" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[151,234,189,212]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="523">Saurita</emphasis>
Herrich-Schäffer, 
<number box="[452,511,188,213]" pageId="18" pageNumber="523" value="1855.0">1855</number>
</taxonomicName>
, which seems to be polyphyletic. It resembles many species that are currently placed in 
<taxonomicName authority="Hubner" authorityName="Hubner" box="[260,501,223,248]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Chrostosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="523" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[260,409,223,248]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="523">Chrostosoma</emphasis>
Hübner
</taxonomicName>
, [
<number box="[519,582,224,248]" pageId="18" pageNumber="523" value="1819.0">1819</number>
], such as 
<taxonomicName authority="Draudt, 1915" authorityName="Draudt" authorityYear="1915" box="[689,939,223,248]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Chrostosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="523" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fassli">
<emphasis box="[689,781,223,248]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="523">C. fassli</emphasis>
Draudt, 
<number box="[880,939,223,248]" pageId="18" pageNumber="523" value="1915.0">1915</number>
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName authority="Dyar, 1916" authorityName="Dyar" authorityYear="1916" box="[997,1294,223,248]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Chrostosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="523" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tabascensis">
<emphasis box="[997,1158,223,248]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="523">C. tabascensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Dyar" box="[1166,1294,223,248]" pageId="18" pageNumber="523" refString="Dyar, H. G. (1916) Descriptions of new Lepidoptera from Mexico. Proceedings of the United States National Museum, 51, 5 - 37." type="journal article" year="1916">
